author: Cillian Sherlock
title: Irish doctors returning home to help with virus crisis
description: A group of Irish doctors in Australia is finally returning to Ireland to help with the Covid-19 emergency, following a long search for flights out of Perth.
content:
A group of Irish doctors in Australia is finally returning to Ireland after a long search for flights out of Perth.
